<li>1994&#160;: <a href="/w/index.php?title=William_F._Meggers_Award_in_Spectroscopy&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="William F. Meggers Award in Spectroscopy (page inexistante)">William F. Meggers Award in Spectroscopy</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_F._Meggers_Award_in_Spectroscopy" class="extiw" title="en:William F. Meggers Award in Spectroscopy"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;William F. Meggers Award in Spectroscopy&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a><sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>4<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1994&#160;: <a href="/w/index.php?title=Arthur_L._Schawlow_Prize_in_Laser_Science&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Arthur L. Schawlow Prize in Laser Science (page inexistante)">Arthur L. Schawlow Prize in Laser Science</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_L._Schawlow_Prize_in_Laser_Science" class="extiw" title="en:Arthur L. Schawlow Prize in Laser Science"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;Arthur L. Schawlow Prize in Laser Science&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a><sup id="cite_ref-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-5"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>5<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1995&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Prix_de_recherche_Humboldt" title="Prix de recherche Humboldt">Prix de recherche Humboldt</a><sup id="cite_ref-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-6"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>6<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
